# Bedrock Manager

Minecraft Bedrock server management app built with NextJS 15, React 19, Docker.

## Development

```bash
npm run dev:start    # Start containers + hot reload
npm run test         # Run integration tests
npm run all-checks   # Lint + type check
npm run dev:stop     # Clean up
```

## Workflow
1. `npm run dev:start` - Start dev environment
2. Code (hot reload enabled)
3. `npm run test` - Test against running containers
4. `npm run all-checks` - Quality checks
5. **GUI Testing** - Use Puppeteer MCP tools to test UI
6. `npm run dev:stop` - Clean up

## Testing
Minimal tests for maximum confidence. Tests hit running containers, check API responses, observe side effects in the containers.

